name: Baxton_Studio_Hypatia_Mid-century_Modern_Grey_Fabric_Walnut_Wood_Button-tufted_Accent_Chair_(Set_of_2)
reviews: I was skeptical of the quality when I purchased the chairs and were afraid they may look cheap. Thankfully I was wrong! This chair set looks awesome and they are super comfortable. I am pleased with the quality and low price.
description: Express your fondness of mid-century style with this pair of button-tufting and cozy Hypatia Grey Fabric Accent Chair.  Upholstered in polyester fabric providing exceptional softness and durability, the walnut finishing solid rubberwood legs, in a strong and sturdy structure, providing a lasting good look and support for the chairs.
